title: AIS helps roll out Oar Inspired technology (ASC - Australian Sports Commission)
text: ( Source : ASC - Australian Sports Commission ) 14 Oct 2015 Australian rowers are set to benefit from a new collaboration between the AIS , Rowing Australia and Brisbane-based company Oar Inspired , which will underpin the rollout of Oar
